item.title: CVE-2023-45111|2024-09-05T19:17:07.135Z -- projectworlds%20pvt.%20limited -- online%20examination%20system
item.description: Online Examination System v1.0 is vulnerable to multiple Unauthenticated SQL Injection vulnerabilities. The 'email' parameter of the feed.php resource does not validate the characters received and they are sent unfiltered to the database.
